    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the project credibility plan consistent with MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as fit for purpose for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all five operating points.",
